      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/34/1/40/753",
      "text": [
        " ثَوْبٍ وَ لَيْسَ مَعَهُ غَيْرُهُ وَ لاَ يَقْدِرُ عَلَى غَسْلِهِ قَالَ «يُصَلِّي فِيهِ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.753 - He was asked by Abd al-Rahman ibn Abi 'Abdillah about a man who becomes ritually impure (junub) in a garment and has no other garment and is unable to wash it.\nImam (as) said: \"He should pray in it.\""
        ]
      }
